      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This FD3S chassis remains a masterclass in lightweight engineering and 50/50 weight distribution. Under the hood, the 13B-REW sequential twin-turbocharged rotary engine pulls strongly through the entire powerband, benefiting from a recently overhauled vacuum line system to ensure seamless transition between primary and secondary boost phases. Power is delivered through a precise five-speed manual gearbox to a Torsen limited-slip differential. To address the platform's known thermal management requirements, an upgraded dual-pass aluminum radiator and silicone coolant hoses have been installed. The double-wishbone suspension remains tight, providing exceptional lateral grip and communicative feedback. While the exterior displays minor road-going patina, the structural integrity and mechanical vitals are robust, making this an ideal driver\u2019s car for those who prioritize kinematic excellence.",
      "price": 34850.0,
